1783620606681593	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyyhQ		item.create	bn-3rst	{"description":"From bn-rah2 item 2. The exclude complaint doesn't reproduce (gix status honors .gitignore/.git/info/exclude/core.excludesFile like git). Real gap: the refusal at crates/maw-cli/src/workspace/sync/checks.rs:194 ('has uncommitted changes that would be lost by sync. Commit or stash first.') discards the StatusEntry paths workspace_has_uncommitted_changes (checks.rs:74) already collected. Print the offending paths (capped, e.g. first 10 + '...and N more') so an operator can distinguish orphaned work from junk scratch. Test: refusal output lists the dirty path.","kind":"task","labels":["bn-rah2-followup"],"size":"xs","title":"ws sync refusal names the offending dirty paths"}	blake3:IU81ZnJBz0F6HrwsbtoJw7Ig-HsJ32wIBdkFdXNdnYQ
